This plugin will automatically convert these supported _DailyMotion_ link and URL in the page and comment content to _DailyMotion_ video player:

 - `https://www.dailymotion.com/video/{$id}`
 - `https://www.dailymotion.com/embed/video/{$id}`
 - `https://dai.ly/{$id}`

The _DailyMotion_ link and URL must be written on its own line by itself, with or without the `www`, with `http://` or `https://`.

All of [the available _DailyMotion_ player parameters](https://developer.dailymotion.com/player#player-parameters) can be used normally and will be applied automatically to the generated video frames.

### Additional Parameters

Name | Description
---- | -----------
`width` | Set custom video width.
`height` | Set custom video height.

**Example:**

~~~ .txt
https://www.dailymotion.com/video/{$id}?width=600&height=250
https://www.dailymotion.com/video/{$id}?width=600px&height=250px
https://www.dailymotion.com/video/{$id}?height=25%
~~~